The old saying to deal with yourself is strong, as is the feeling of being perceived as a weak person if you talk openly about problems.
Friends is one of the series that comes to mind when I try to offer more mechanisms of psychological adaptation in the long term.
The show highlighted the small moments of friendship between men.
As much as objective, external intervention helps, through the phone, people reached in moments of despair, long-term support comes from family and close friends.
