Why would refugees settle in another country from which they are fleeing?
But what produces much wonder is especially the hypocrisy with which such a crisis is dealt with.
We are first hitting on the warlike hypocrisy of the strong EU states, which show the utmost generosity when it comes to sharing troubles with smaller countries.
